      "content": "makes sense. what if a tech journalist starts digging and asks specifically if any data was actually \"exposed\" to the public internet? should we tell them the truth about the S3 bucket configuration, or is it better to stick to the 'synchronization hiccup' narrative to avoid a PR nightmare?",
